			<a href="http://www.iunknown.com/2008/03/henrys-adventur.html#comment-106989832">March 14, 2008 at 08:17 AM</a>
		</p>
	</div>
	<a id="c107021216"></a>
	<div class="comment" id="comment-107021216">
		<div class="comment-content">
			<p>Where's the conflict in the story where Henry learns some 'life lesson?'</p>

<p>;)</p>

<p>Almost perfect Thomas the Tank Engine story....</p>

<p>In your copious spare time you could throw together a Powerpoint slideshow with the pictures and text and print it out to read to Ben.</p>

<p>Hmmm. I'll have to do that on my next business trip...</p>
